    "id": 1,
    "attributes": {
      "title": "The New Covenant",
      "slug": "the-new-covenant",
      "content": "",
      "componentIds": [],
      "published": false,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "<p>Some time ago we started a series of articles focused on the issue of the great conflict between God and Satan. It is our intention to compile these articles and make them into a book entitled, “<strong>The Mother of all Wars.</strong>”&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "<p><span style=\"color: var(--color-graphite);\">The topics dealt with up to this point are outlined below. </span></p><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Origins and Issues</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">The foundations</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Corporate identity and sin</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">The curse</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">God’s amazing solution</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Unfinished business</span></li></ol><p><br></p>"
        }
      ]
    }
